data.description: Quaint Newly renovated 3 bed/ 2 bath home for sale in Croissant Park, close to Downtown Fort Lauderdale, Las Olas, Beaches, Mall, Shopping Restaurants, minutes to Airport, 95/595 & Turnpike.Home features an expansive lot with potential for expansion, pool, or another unit in the back: RD-15 Zoning allowance for up to 2 units, fruit trees. Impact windows throughout and a 2 year old water heater. 1 year old washer and dryer. Stainless Steel appliances, lots of beautiful highly functional wooden cabinets and granite counter tops. Living area has a well lit open floor plan. This Great Opportunity won't last. Make us an offer today!
